## 🚨 CRITICAL RULES (Must Follow)

### 1. Client-Side Data Fetching: ALWAYS Use React Query + Axios

**⚠️ OVERRIDE**: This rule OVERRIDES the SWR recommendation from `.cursor/skills/vercel-react-best-practices/rules/client-swr-dedup.md`. We use **React Query (TanStack Query)** + **Axios** instead of SWR.

**❌ NEVER DO THIS:**pescript
// WRONG: useState + useEffect + fetch pattern
function ContractsPage() {
  const [contracts, setContracts] = useState([]);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);
  
  useEffect(() => {
    contractsApi.list()
      .then(setContracts)
      .finally(() => setLoading(false));
  }, []);
}
